<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA512_04_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema512_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema512_04_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">28과 42의 최대공약수를 두 가지 방법으로 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box">
          <div class="question_block left">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="row">
                28=2×2×
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field></div>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                42=2×3×
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">
              <div class="row gap_20">
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA512_04_IH/0002_img01.png" alt="" width="40" />
                <span lang="y">28과 42의 최대공약수:</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row mt_25 gap_10">
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field></div>
                ×
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field></div>
                =
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="question_block right">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="row">
                <span class="num left">2</span>
                <span class="num">28</span>
                <span class="num">4</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="input_wrap left"><math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field></div>
                <span class="num">14</span>
                <span class="num">21</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <span class="num">2</span>
                <div class="input_wrap right"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">
              <div class="row gap_20">
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA512_04_IH/0002_img01.png" alt="" width="40" />
                <span lang="y">28과 42의 최대공약수:</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row mt_25 gap_10">
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field></div>
                ×
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field></div>
                =
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">식에 공통으로 들어 있는 수를 모두 곱하면 되므로 두 수의 최대공약수는 2×7=14입니다.</p>
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">28과 42의 최대공약수는 두 수를 나눈 공약수들의 곱이므로 2×7=14입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
